## Phase 4: Causal Inference Engine

### [NEW] `backend/app/ai_module/causal/discovery.py`

- Wraps `causal-learn`'s PC algorithm
- Input: Time-series matrix of metrics for **anomalous services only** (pre-filtered by GNN scores > threshold)
- Output: Causal DAG over the anomalous subset

### [NEW] `backend/app/ai_module/causal/validate.py`

- Cross-validates causal edges against the actual dependency graph
- Removes spurious causal edges that contradict known service topology
- Extracts root cause candidates (nodes with no incoming causal edges from other anomalous nodes)

